'''''Galunker''''' is a children's novel by [[Douglas Anthony Cooper]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.huffingtonpost.com/douglas-anthony-cooper/galunker-part-1_b_5393410.html|title=Galunker, a Picture Book About a Pit Bull|first=Douglas Anthony|last=Cooper|date=27 May 2014|publisher=|accessdate=2 July 2018}}</ref><ref name="auto">{{cite web|url=https://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/pit-bulls-bigotry-and-a-book_us_5a2abfe1e4b022ec613b819f|title=Pit Bulls, Bigotry And A Book|first=Douglas Anthony|last=Cooper|date=8 December 2017|publisher=|accessdate=2 July 2018}}</ref>, Illustrated by Dula Yavne
==Conception==
The book was funded by raising money by [[Kickstarter]] it raised $55,000 to get a publishing run.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.huffingtonpost.com/douglas-anthony-cooper/a-childrens-book-about-a-_b_5453984.html|title=A Children's Book About a Pit Bull???|first=Douglas Anthony|last=Cooper|date=5 June 2014|publisher=|accessdate=3 July 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.huffingtonpost.com/douglas-anthony-cooper/ignorance-kills-one-milli_b_5528603.html|title=Ignorance Kills One Million Pit Bulls per Year|first=Douglas Anthony|last=Cooper|date=25 June 2014|publisher=|accessdate=3 July 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/controversial-kickstarter-hit-galunker---a-childrens-book-about-a-pit-bull-265188761.html|title= Controversial Kickstarter hits Galunker|website=www.prnewswire.com|accessdate=4 July 2018}}</ref> <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/galunker-a-childrens-book-to-change-our-perception-of-pit-bulls-260748961.html|title=GALUNKER: A Children's Book to Change Our Perception of Pit Bulls|website=www.prnewswire.com|accessdate=4 July 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://globalnews.ca/news/1423931/childrens-book-about-pit-bull-raises-more-than-55k-on-kickstarter/|title=Children’s book about pit bull raises more than $55k on Kickstarter|publisher=|accessdate=5 July 2018}}</ref> The original target was $27,000.
==Plot== {{More plot|section|date=July 2018}}
The book is about Galunker a misunderstood [[pitbull]] who seeks a home after a lifetime of [[dog fighting]] .<ref name="auto1"/>
