'''Lacus Hiemalis''' ([[Latin]] for "Lake of Winter") is a small [[lunar mare]] in the [[Terra Nivium]] region on the [[Moon]]. It is located at 15.0° N, 14.0° E and is 50&nbsp;km in diameter.

